casebody.data:
In re Resignation of Sheldon.

[Cite as In re Resignation of Sheldon (1989), 43 Ohio St. 3d 604.]

(No. 89-572 Submitted April 11, 1989 Decided May 17, 1989.)

The resignation of Carey S. Sheldon as an attorney is accepted.

Moyer, C.J., Sweeney, Holmes, Douglas, Wright, H. Brown and Resnick, JJ., concur.
